<div style="background-color:  #E5C6F5">
  <h2>System Alert: this Saved Items system is going away December 23, 2023</h2>
  <p>NYU Libraries is moving to a new catalog system, with a new saved items tool.</p>
  <p>The ability to save items from the catalog will be unavailable from Monday November 13, 2023 - January 4, 2024.</p>
  <p>As an alternative, please plan to use your preferred citation management tools or the catalog's email function.</p>
  <p>Unfortunately, we cannot migrate existing saved items (those added up until Nov 13, 2023) to the new system.</p>
  <p>You can get a list of the current saved items in your library account up until Friday, December 23, 2023. After that date this system will not be available.
  How to export to email or other citation management tools - FAQ for BobCat "Saved Items" (E-Shelf) Retirement (Google Doc).</p>
</div>
<div id="controls" class="btn-toolbar js">
  <%= button_dropdown(select_title, select_options, false) %>
  <div class="btn-group"><%= link_to(t('record.collection.delete.title_html'), records_path, data: { confirm: t('record.collection.delete.confirmation_html') }, method: :delete, id: "delete", class: "btn btn-danger") %></div>
  <%= button_dropdown(t('record.collection.email.title_html'), email_options) %>
  <%= button_dropdown(t('record.collection.print.title_html'), print_options) %>
  <%= button_dropdown(t('record.collection.export.title_html'), export_options) %>
  <%= right_button_dropdown(t('record.collection.sort.title_html') + " ".html_safe + current_sort_label, sort_options)%>
  <%= right_button_dropdown(content_tag(:span, "#{per_page} ") + t('record.collection.per_page.title_html'), per_page_options)%>
</div>
